text][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;60px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content&#8221; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673906832489{margin-right: 80px !important;margin-left: 80px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/3&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673906879372{margin-top: 25px !important;padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 80px !important;padding-left: 80px !important;}&#8221;]<span style=\"font-family: 'Paytone One'; font-size: 24pt; color: #808b91;\">What An RBT Does<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Provides one-on-one Applied Behavior Analysis (ABA) services to clients.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Implements individualized treatment plans which include behavioral skill acquisition and behavior reduction protocols.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Communicates and collaborates with parents\/caregivers, teachers, and others to ensure consistency and continuity of care during and outside of sessions.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Collects and records data to monitor clients\u2019 progress and effectiveness of treatment plan.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Follows data collection procedures with accuracy.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Provides feedback and insight to client\u2019s lead therapist regarding client\u2019s needs and changes in behavior based on what is seen while providing direct services.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Maintains the highest standard of ethics, including confidentiality.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Creates a safe, positive and fun environment to encourage learning.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;12319&#8243; img_size=&#8221;large&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css_animation=&#8221;rollIn&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673896052444{margin-top: 30px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;}&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row_content&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673906840789{margin-right: 80px !important;margin-left: 80px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673906845911{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 80px !important;background-color: #99c243 !important;}&#8221;]<span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: 'Paytone One'; font-size: 24pt;\">RBT Position Summary<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;4\/5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673706743845{margin-right: 120px !important;margin-left: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 32px !important;}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622751158862\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622748257804\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622751158862\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622751158862\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622748257804\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Kidz Companion, Inc. provides in-home ABA services for children and young adults with ASD or other developmental disabilities.\u00a0\u00a0We are seeking Registered Behavior Technicians to join our team and provide services in home and school settings. Our ideal candidate must be tireless and adaptable in his or her ability to create an environment so children and young adults can adapt and thrive in any environment.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1622748277686\">\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\n<p class=\"carrier-title\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">An RBT Candidate must:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"blackbullet\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be energetic (able to maintain enthusiasm for a 4+ hour session).<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be precise in following procedures and instructions, both written and spoken.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be able to provide feedback and insight to client\u2019s lead therapist regarding client\u2019s needs and changes in behavior based on what is seen while providing direct services.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Communicate with all members of the team, with the goal of improving services and maintaining procedural integrity.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be responsive to the needs and requests of clients, their families, and supervisors.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be goal-oriented and maintain professionalism in all aspects of work.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Maintain the highest standard of ethics, including confidentiality.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Have excellent written and verbal communication skills.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be able to accept instruction and constructive criticism (and use both to improve therapeutic skills).<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Have a basic understanding of technology (such as iPads and Microsoft Office).<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Be physically able to respond quickly from any position, walk quickly or jog short distances, stand on feet for a minimum of 15 minutes, and lift (up to 50lbs).<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Have personal means of transportation with a reliable vehicle.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: 'Barlow Semi Condensed'; font-size: 14pt; color: #7f7f7f;\">Services may be provided to support activities of daily living, communication and social skills.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/5&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1647294829038{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1673703988985{margin-right: 30px !important;padding-top: 20px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;background-color: #e7e6e6 !important;}&#8221;]<span sty